    "Deleting all data permanently removes all your travels and completed stops. Your progress, XP, badges, and achievements will all be lost and this cannot be undone. Export a backup first via Settings > Data Management." : {
      "comment" : "FAQ: delete data answer",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
