            "value" : "L'ANNÉE EN CHIFFRES"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Yes! All transit data is bundled with the app so you can browse lines, stations, and routes without an internet connection." : {
      "comment" : "FAQ: offline answer",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Yes! All transit data is bundled with the app so you can browse lines, stations, and routes without an internet connection."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Oui ! Toutes les données de transport sont intégrées à l'application afin que vous puissiez consulter les lignes, les arrêts et les itinéraires sans connexion Internet."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Yes. Go to Profile > History, tap Select, choose the travels you want to remove, then delete them. If a stop is no longer covered by another travel on that line, it will also be removed from your completion." : {
      "comment" : "FAQ: delete travel answer",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Yes. Go to Profile > History, tap Select, choose the travels you want to remove, then delete them. If a stop is no longer covered by another travel on that line, it will also be removed from your completion."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Oui. Allez dans Profil > Historique, appuyez sur Sélectionner, choisissez les trajets que vous souhaitez retirer, puis supprimez-les. Si un arrêt n'est plus couvert par un autre trajet sur cette ligne, il sera également retiré de votre progression."
          }
        }
      }
    },
